window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Sinfully sexy bar owner Dylan has a thing for needy women. He's a savior, a knight in shining armor, and his mighty talented sword has no trouble bringing damsels in distress to their knees. Enter Tiffany Winters, a gorgeous cutthroat sports agent who looks like sex on legs, f--ks like she's passion personified, and wouldn't let a man help her if she were dangling from a ledge and he was her only hope. One night and too much tequila might change their lives forever. The question is, will either one survive? </p> <p>The Billionaires After Dark series is part of the Love in Bloom romance collection. Each book may be enjoyed as a stand-alone novel, or as part of the series. </p>"; 
